{"tid":2132287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［對唔住再開過］沈旭輝： 被DQ既議員照分析應該不再被特首委任下年既緊急議會","createTime":"2020-07-30T09:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T11:39:21.000Z","uid":22556,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02305655274dceb54f35c8b01f9f4421415679c0","tid":2132287,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"【#Patreon突發時空🇭🇰】根據這些基準，DQ的絕對肯定不止12人：勝出初選的「抗爭派」、「本土派」非常可能一律被DQ。對民主黨候選人的決定（他們不少也表態否決財政預算），就是下一個指標。對政權而言，相信上述決定有下列目的：<br />\n<br />\n1. 宣示新紅線，除了確保任何未來要選舉的人都會遵守，也令越過紅線的人擔心會否同時有違反國安法風險，從而達到社會全盤收緊的目的。<br />\n2. 非建制派自然會分裂為兩大意見：Plan B/C/D 也要繼續選，與及從此杯葛一切選舉。<br />\n3. <strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">假如9月選舉延遲一年，由特首委任「緊急議會」，這些被DQ的現任議員，自然也「不應」再被委任。屆時這屆「議會」的組成，真的類似1997-1998年的臨時立法會，可以通過任何爭議議案（例如明日大嶼）。</span></span></strong><br />\n4. 向國際社會宣示「底線思維」。<br />\n<br />\n由於這是加速主義的典型，往後發展，肯定超乎想像，並即時出現五大問題...... <br />\n<br />\n⏺全文見Patreon<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/39874670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F39874670&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSiTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=2fbc446c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/39874670</a>"},{"pid":"0d075c65b0a45350c8f54915dcdbe79aba699274","tid":2132287,"uid":362015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3715c203301e3ea1a3c1dddad282447e8cd27d24","tid":2132287,"uid":21602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"35+都唔可能，最怕佢唔dq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e835eaebb83d57adde990fab447ea77b0993b01","tid":2132287,"uid":38317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:02:10.000Z","msg":"都話明日大愚